    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for the VAD hemolysis COU is accepted as a complete submission for regulatory review. All thirteen credibility factors have been addressed in accordance with the Minimal profile declaration. Seven factors were formally assessed; six factors were identified as epistemic gaps at Model Risk Level 5. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification provides partial coverage of input uncertainty per project requirements. The overall assurance level is Low and the substantive decision on model adequacy remains Not accepted pending resolution of the identified factor gaps, but the package itself satisfies submission completeness criteria under the Minimal profile.",
